snippet.title: Strashna 2 Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Strashna 2 is a horror game where you explore a large mansion in search of clues and discover different locations where you need to escape from monsters and solve puzzles.

Music created by Sooma

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2756580/Strashna_2/
